---
// src/components/curso/ProjectsSection.astro
---

<section
    class="px-6 lg:px-20 py-20 bg-[#0b0e14] border-y border-white/5"
    id="proyectos"
>
    <div
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center"
    >
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative animate-fade-in-left">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <img
                    alt="Trabajo en equipo de marketing"
                    class="rounded-xl shadow-lg"
                    data-alt="Marketing team brainstorming in a modern office"
                    src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBPO2ZrjHQ0hfoYAHmXMrnrrCFfTrgHtTWSepGhkj5Mw14ZAEzkHObH-Si5nnF8egY_2L4eeyXv4C4gi6HY9ZOa2QoioddZW_IcPCu_aOZGQSBmyh2Elwzv1PhwO8gJD8UXiCYmHPK6sOkdqQNQxac_jRhCbQatlVF6SFFgsHu-Bff4T6AXRD3M36O_ZKJxBbZT1ZFRwSi1cNbjKgmt0IMKUq0fufNbpWTMnGsF3njcTiIChywMAu2KTBwYZjmIdC7LvK07yPMODQ"
                />
                <img
                    alt="Profesional analizando datos"
                    class="rounded-xl shadow-lg translate-y-12"
                    data-alt="Young professional working on laptop with charts"
                    src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA0auTsj-lIDdEl3qDDMyoaG9hhxO6Zfgv4zNiCPytsppMNyLISxY-AI0qPF8ePLrEApUoLsABeSnPrOLMg50MLaiVYwYTtFTdkVHU_3BhwGdXzAIAVuM0XyZ0bQEXonqJBH9ARhnGuzdjacP4Zhe2ki6yEvDJrZKGgBbOHpxYLXl8WPvnF2_T6t3lgX120HSQjWRafpLbiPC3ZJbwk7YfuQUSKqR4gKzY5pPui_U7aKaL49GCEbkTB0Qiz97GxQ8RaTDie4N5k_g"
                />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 animate-fade-in-right">
            <h2
                class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
            >
                Proyectos Reales, <br />Experiencia de Verdad
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg mb-8">
                No simulamos el trabajo. Te asignamos retos de empresas
                asociadas que necesitan soluciones de marketing actuales.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div
                    class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                        >groups</span
                    >
                    <p class="font-medium">
                        Creación de contenido viral para marcas de retail.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                        >campaign</span
                    >
                    <p class="font-medium">
                        Lanzamiento de campañas de captación en Google y Meta
                        Ads.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                        >architecture</span
                    >
                    <p class="font-medium">
                        Estructura de estrategias omnicanal B2B.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                        >bar_chart_4_bars</span
                    >
                    <p class="font-medium">
                        Análisis profundo de competidores usando datasets de IA.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
